Algorithm

Step 1: Start
Step 2: Set Date and time in Lcd Display
Step 3: If Button pressed
		Goto Step 4
	Else
		Goto step 2
Step 4:get the current location
Step 5:current location and user information send to authorized authority
step 6:tTacke the video and store to sd card
step7:goto step 1 //Repeat the process
